      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;proxmox--automatically-restore-smbcifs-share-connections&#34;&gt;Proxmox | automatically restore SMB/CIFS share connections&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If at some point Proxmox loses connectivity with an SMB/CIFS share, it will not restore the connection by itself until a restart of the Proxmox node is performed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With this tip, you’ll make the Proxmox node restore the connection automatically.&lt;/p&gt;
